##################################
# DOCUMENTATION - KEEP PUBLIC
##################################

# These are GOOD to commit:
# ✅ *.md (Markdown documentation)
# ✅ *.rst (ReStructuredText)
# ✅ docs/ (Documentation folder)
# ✅ examples/ (Public examples only)
# ✅ README files
# ✅ CONTRIBUTING.md
# ✅ CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
# ✅ LICENSE

##################################
# PUBLIC API SPECS (KEEP)
##################################

# These should be committed:
# ✅ openapi.yaml
# ✅ swagger.json
# ✅ api_reference.md
# ✅ API examples (no real credentials)

